---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About Alex Janiak" description="Alex Janiak is a startup founder building AI forecasting systems for better decision-making under uncertainty. He writes about forecasting, futarchy, decision markets, mechanism design, game theory, AI, and philosophy.">
	<h1 class="page-title">About</h1>

	<div class="about-intro">
		<img class="about-tree" src="/about-tree.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="1024" height="1536" />

		<p><span class="newthought">Hi! I'm Alex Janiak</span>, a startup founder building AI forecasting systems for better decision-making under uncertainty. I am interested in mechanism design, systems engineering, rational decision-making, and the parts of philosophy that start where clean formalism runs out: Nagel, Wittgenstein, post-rationalism, and the subjectivity stuff.</p>

		<p>This blog is working notes on those themes — forecasting, futarchy, prediction markets, game theory, and the strange philosophical edges around how people turn models of the world into action.</p>

	</div>

